    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessemus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/186" key="#Princeps">Sichardus</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3633" key="#Intercessory #Principissa"
                            >Adelgise</persName> dilecte dilecte coniugis nostre tibi <name
                            ref="Autulus">Autulo</name>
                        <rs key="#Gold #Specialized_workers">aurifeci</rs>nostro <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >rem illas</rs> in <placeName ref="#places/3464"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                            >Folianense</placeName> quas <name ref="Allo">Allo</name><rs
                            key="#Freeborn"> liber homo</rs>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >infiduciatas aut in pigno tenuit a <rs key="#Slave">servi</rs> sacri
                            nostri palatii</rs>, et <name ref="Dominicus">Dominicus</name>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Slave"
                            >servus</rs> nostri palatii cum uxoria et filiis cum suis cispitibus de
                        Folianense, de <rs key="#Actio">actu</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3634" key="#Marepahis">Attionis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marepahis">maripahis</rs> nostri, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo
                        et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum prereceptum prephata omnia que superius
                        legitur tu et heredes tui possideatis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id
                        est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3462" key="#Writer">Theodericus</persName>. Actum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/3436">Abellino</placeName> sexto
                        anno, mense ianuario, prima indictio. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
